predict_diagnosis:
1. Arrhythmogenic right ventricular dysplasia (ARVD/C)
2. Familial hypertrophic cardiomyopathy (FHC)
3. Idiopathic restrictive cardiomyopathy (IRCM)
4. Dilated cardiomyopathy (DCM)
5. Myocarditis
6. Atrial septal defect (ASD) or atrial fibrillation (AF) with embolic stroke
7. Heart failure with preserved ejection fraction (HFpEF)
8. Valvular heart disease (VHD), specifically tricuspid valve disease
9. Congenital heart disease (CHD), possibly right ventricular outflow tract obstruction
10. Systemic lupus erythematosus (SLE) or other autoimmune disease affecting the heart
